THE PRICE!

28
00:04:08,708 --> 00:04:10,291
- ( growls )

29
00:04:10,375 --> 00:04:12,416
- ( grunts, wheezes )

30
00:04:18,708 --> 00:04:20,708
- ( ragged breathing )

31
00:04:27,375 --> 00:04:28,708
( whimpers )

32
00:04:28,791 --> 00:04:31,208
- WE'RE GOING TO HAVE TO WALK
ONCE WE PASS THE RIVER.

33
00:04:31,291 --> 00:04:33,875
