TO LEAVE WITHOUT US.

36
00:04:43,833 --> 00:04:47,083
BEING A PRO IS MORE THAN JUST
BRINGING DOWN YOUR TARGET.

37
00:04:47,166 --> 00:04:49,833
MAKING A CLEAN GETAWAY IS
THE MARK OF A PROFESSIONAL.

38
00:04:49,916 --> 00:04:51,916
YOU KNOW THAT AS WELL AS--

39
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,916
( gasps )
- ( chiming )

40
00:04:56,041 --> 00:04:57,666
- ( sighs )

41
00:05:00,083 --> 00:05:01,750
- ( whimpering )

42
00:05:01,833 --> 00:05:05,416
- ARE YOU--
- NO, I'M FINE.

43
00:05:07,125 --> 00:05:09,125
- STILL, ON THE BRIGHTER SIDE,

44
00:05:09,208 --> 00:05:12,208
IF YOU HAD BEEN KILLED, AT LEAST
I WOULD HAVE BEEN FREE OF YOU.

45
00:05:13,333 --> 00:05:14,791
- THAT'S TRUE.

46
00:05:14,875 --> 00:05:18,625
- ( woman singing in bathroom )

47
00:05:38,083 --> 00:05:39,791
- ( silenced gunshots )

48
