53
00:06:01,166 --> 00:06:04,666
- YEAH, THEY SAY HE'S SCARIER
THAN THE GRIM REAPER.

54
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:06,791
- HMM?

55
00:06:06,875 --> 00:06:09,000
( groans )

56
00:06:09,083 --> 00:06:11,041
THE REAPER?

57
