THE TORTURES OF HELL!

60
00:06:19,625 --> 00:06:22,208
WE'LL DRAG THIS REAPER
INTO THE DESERT SUN

61
00:06:22,291 --> 00:06:24,333
AND STAKE HIM OUT TO DIE!

62
00:06:36,916 --> 00:06:38,750
- ( panting )

63
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:56,541
- MIREILLE,
MY I.D. CARD.

64
00:06:56,625 --> 00:06:59,875
- HUH?
