67
00:07:05,833 --> 00:07:07,875
BUT I COULDN'T
THROW IT AWAY

68
00:07:07,958 --> 00:07:11,166
EVEN THOUGH I KNEW

69
00:07:11,250 --> 00:07:13,375
IT WASN'T REAL,

70
00:07:13,458 --> 00:07:15,875
THAT IT WASN'T THE REAL ME

71
00:07:15,958 --> 00:07:18,375
OR ANYTHING. I...

72
00:07:18,458 --> 00:07:20,833
- JUST BE QUIET.
- ( grunts )

73
00:07:20,916 --> 00:07:22,916
- THIS ISN'T THE TIME
FOR THAT NOW.

74
00:07:33,833 --> 00:07:37,291
- Kirika: WHEN I CAME TO,
I WAS IN THIS PLACE.

75
00:07:40,250 --> 00:07:43,583
MY NAME AND ALL MY RECORDS,

76
