CARE LESS ABOUT YOU

100
00:10:48,500 --> 00:10:50,708
OR WHO YOU REALLY ARE,

101
00:10:50,791 --> 00:10:54,125
BUT YOU'RE MY KEY
TO FINDING THE SOLDATS.

102
00:10:54,208 --> 00:10:57,083
SO UNTIL I FIND OUT
WHO THEY ARE,

103
00:10:57,166 --> 00:10:59,625
I'M NOT GOING
TO LET YOU DIE.

104
00:10:59,708 --> 00:11:01,958
BUT ONCE I'VE FOUND THEM OUT...

105
00:11:03,541 --> 00:11:05,625
I WILL KILL YOU.

106
00:11:08,791 --> 00:11:10,416
- I'D FORGOTTEN.

107
00:11:14,083 --> 00:11:16,000
- HEY, LOOK AT THIS!
- DID YOU FIND SOMETHING?

108
00:11:16,083 --> 00:11:17,250
