( gasps )

114
00:12:46,333 --> 00:12:48,333
- ( men scream, grunt )

115
00:12:49,791 --> 00:12:51,208
- WE'VE GOT HIM!

116
00:12:51,291 --> 00:12:53,250
- IT'S A GIRL.

117
00:12:53,333 --> 00:12:55,208
- IT'S HER, LOOK AT THE WOUND.

118
00:12:55,291 --> 00:12:57,041
- BUT SHE'S JUST A KID!

119
00:13:08,291 --> 00:13:10,041
- HUH?

120
00:13:11,333 --> 00:13:13,000
WHAT'S THIS?

121
00:13:17,458 --> 00:13:19,583
- ( whimpers )

122
00:13:19,666 --> 00:13:21,333
- TAKE HER TO IZUDDIN.

123
00:13:21,416 --> 00:13:23,041
- YES, IT WILL BE DONE, SIR!

124
00:13:23,125 --> 00:13:26,208
