126
00:13:38,458 --> 00:13:41,333
- ( music-box melody playing )

127
00:13:54,208 --> 00:13:56,500
- ( ticking )

128
00:14:03,541 --> 00:14:06,708
- ( ticking echoes )

129
00:14:16,208 --> 00:14:19,125
