THEY'RE NOT SPENDING
THEIR MONEY RIGHT.

135
00:15:08,291 --> 00:15:11,125
- WHAT? WHAT'S WRONG WITH OUR
COMMUNICATION SYSTEM?

136
00:15:11,208 --> 00:15:14,375
- I'LL TELL YOU-- MY GIRLFRIEND,
SHE HAS THIS CELLPHONE.

137
00:15:14,458 --> 00:15:16,416
