- ( both grunt )

141
00:15:34,541 --> 00:15:36,041
- HMM.

142
00:15:36,125 --> 00:15:38,250
- ( engine starts )

143
00:15:42,291 --> 00:15:46,125
- ( choir singing in Latin )

144
00:15:51,333 --> 00:15:54,583
- IT IS THE NAME
OF AN ANCIENT FATE--

145
00:15:54,666 --> 00:15:57,666
TWO MAIDENS
WHO GOVERN DEATH.

146
00:15:57,750 --> 00:16:00,666
TO THE DEPTHS
OF HELL'S FIRE,

147
00:16:00,750 --> 00:16:04,250
THEIR BLACK SOULS
LURE THE LOST CHILDREN.

148
00:16:15,416 --> 00:16:17,958
- ( flames crackling )

149
00:16:28,458 --> 00:16:30,291
- THIS IS THE REAPER?

150
00:16:30,375 --> 00:16:34,291
- OH, SHE IS CONNECTED TO NOIR.
THERE IS NO DOUBT.

151
00:16:34,375 --> 00:16:36,791
- WHAT, THIS LITTLE GIRL?!

152
00:16:36,875 --> 00:16:40,125
- I AM SURE. SHE REEKS
OF THE SCENT OF DEATH.

153
00:16:40,208 --> 00:16:41,791
- ( footsteps )

154
00:16:44,083 --> 00:16:46,291
( gasps )
IT'S HER!

155
00:16:52,000 --> 00:16:53,416
