163
00:17:18,416 --> 00:17:22,041
- YOU ARE BRAVE,
BUT YOU'LL CONFESS.

164
00:17:22,125 --> 00:17:26,250
YOU'LL CONFESS AS YOU ROAST
IN THE FIRES OF HELL ITSELF.

165
00:17:28,666 --> 00:17:29,791
( chuckles )

166
00:17:31,416 --> 00:17:32,666
( stomps )
- ( yelps )

167
00:17:32,750 --> 00:17:34,791
- SO THAT CARD'S
PRECIOUS TO YOU, IS IT?

168
00:17:34,875 --> 00:17:38,375
