00:18:47,750 --> 00:18:50,125
- ( cocks )

190
00:18:50,208 --> 00:18:51,625
- ( growls )

191
00:18:56,500 --> 00:18:57,875
- HUH?

192
00:19:07,666 --> 00:19:10,375
- ( gasps )
- COULD IT BE GOVERNMENT TROOPS?

193
00:19:10,458 --> 00:19:12,541
- THERE'S NO WAY!
OUR INFORMANT IN THE ARMY

194
00:19:12,625 --> 00:19:15,250
