00:20:27,375 --> 00:20:29,166
- WHAT IS SHE TALKING ABOUT?

214
00:20:29,250 --> 00:20:31,166
- NOIR...

215
00:20:31,250 --> 00:20:33,625
IT IS THE NAME

216
00:20:33,708 --> 00:20:36,416
OF AN ANCIENT FATE--

217
00:20:36,500 --> 00:20:38,708
TWO MAIDENS

218
00:20:38,791 --> 00:20:41,291
WHO GOVERN DEATH.
